-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>临汾 — 华山 1485 35.5元 18:55~23:16</p>\n<h1>10.2~10.3</h1>\n<p>临汾 — 华山 2671 89.5元 02:54~06:35</p>\n<h2>【陕西】华山</h2>\n<p>华山 — 西安 7~20点都有火车，很便宜，最慢一个小时也到了</p>\n<h1>10.4~10.5 【陕西】西安</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">三门峡  8-21\n   函谷关\n   三门峡大坝\n   豫西大峡谷\n洛阳\n   龙门石窟\n   丽景门\n郑州 火车\n   登封2h 嵩山</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"life"},"fields":{"slug":"/life/2015/09/28/一路向西.html","date":"September 28, 2015","title":"一路向西"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/life/2015/09/28/一路向西.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech fe/2015/08/25/写写fekit extension.html","title":"写写fekit extension"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2015/12/25/esprima静态分析js代码.html","title":"esprima静态分析js代码"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}